<event name="EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL">
	<!-- <preventQuest/> Does this work here? -->
	<text load="TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL"/>
	<store>STORE_RADIKAL</store>
</event>
<textList name="TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL">
	<text>Your sensors stop functioning and your view is suddenly obscured, but apparently that's just the doing of a very cautious and well-equipped band of traders. No wonder, with all the shady business going on around here.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>You can't see any shop in the vicinity, but soon a drone from a very well camouflaged ship takes your order.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>You are quickly scanned and told to stay right here while the owner of a shop that's too far to see arranges remote delivery of your purchases.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>While you wait at the trading spot, a tiny drone entertains you with an endless feed of funny videos.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>You are forced to leave your ship parked outside while you do your shopping closely escorted inside what looked like a random asteroid.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>The clerk here is very quiet. Once you install the goods in your ship, as per the deal you wipe recent records so that the merchant's ship appears to have never been here at all.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
	<text>You reluctantly agree to leave your ship in an empty space matrix before they grant you access to the store, and when you exit it, there is no other ship but yours here.
		
		[Warning: Limited purchases]</text>
</textList>


<!-- <event name="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED" unique="true">, CRASHES the game if allowed to happen twice ! 
If used in eventList, list must have a non-unique option!-->
<FTL>
<event name="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED">
	<preventQuest/>
	<text>Slavers are quite comfortably installed in this sector, in great part due to the lack of regulation. You stumble upon one.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_SLAVER_ALL" hostile="false"/>
	<choice>
		<text>See who they might have for sale.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Feds here? You're surely in need of some muscle, and this might just be your lucky day! We have an elite warrior to do the heavy lifting for you, greatly discounted because we must trade fast and leave for... reasons. What say you?" You notice that the discount is pretty solid indeed, maybe too good.</text> 
			<choice hidden="false">
				<text>Purchase the elite slave.</text>
				<event>
					<text>You hand over the scrap to the slavers...</text> 
					<item_modify>
						<item type="scrap" min="-22" max="-22"/>
					</item_modify>
					
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_OUTCOMES"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Decline.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>

	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Attack the slavers.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Slavery is despicable! You prepare for combat, knowing the elite slave will probably not survive it.</text>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>

	<choice>
		<text>Ignore them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Another ship comes in and buys the slave shortly afterwards. Then it starts going up in flames. Maybe you chose wisely.
			You have some time to yourself.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<eventList name="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_OUTCOMES">
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_LOSTSUN"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_DUSKBRINGER"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_GOUL"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_MANTIS"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_RK_FIREGHOST"/>
	
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_LOSTSUN"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_DUSKBRINGER"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_GOUL"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_MANTIS"/>
	<event load="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_RK_FIREGHOST"/>
</eventList>

<event name="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_LOSTSUN">
	<text>They bring you the slave and remove his restraints, apparently relieved to get rid of him. "I wasn't stuck in there with them. They were stuck in there with me." says the freshly freed troublesome slave. You diplomatically nod and welcome them aboard.</text> 
	<crewMember amount="1" combat="2" class="rock_commando"/>
	<choice>
		<text>I think they'll fit right in.</text>
		<event load="REPUTATION_UPDATE_SLAVER"/>
	</choice>
</event>
