<event name="RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_LOSTSUN">
	<text>They bring you the slave and remove his restraints so quickly that you haven't even transferred all the scrap yet. Unfortunately the troublemaker doesn't seem to like the way some of your crew look at him, and starts punching! 
	You interrupt the scrap transfer and watch the slavers immediately jump away, leaving you to deal with him.</text>
	<item_modify>
		<item type="scrap" min="10" max="20"/>
	</item_modify>
	<instantEscape/>
	
	<boarders min="1" max="1" class="rock_commando"/>
	<choice>
		<text>So that's why he was so cheap.</text>
		<event load="REPUTATION_UPDATE_SLAVER"/>
	</choice>
</event>
