		<event>
			<text>"... yes indeed. Thank you for your cooperation. Remember to pass by the Police Station to cover the post-seizure administrative fees."
			As they finally leave you alone, you wonder whether it would be possible to get your gear back.</text>
			<quest event="ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK"/>
			
			<!-- <variable name="seized_shipvoreram" op="set" val="1"/> -->
			<variable name="seized_shipvoreram" op="add" val="1"/>
			<remove name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM"/>
			<choice>
				<text>...</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM" lvl="1" hidden="true" blue="true">
		<text>'Shipvore Ram [L]'</text>
		<event>
			<text>"... yes indeed. Thank you for your... wait, this contraption is one half of the vessel. It cannot be simply cut out without causing catastrophic failure, and then we would be accused of "police brutality" for ages... These orders are suboptimal, we are special police, not disassembly technicians!"</text>
			
			<choice>
				<text>So... what now?</text>
				<event>
					<text>"...Just... Hmmm. Pay the fine. No, we're not currently assigned to fining duties... I do not wish to deal with another 'unlawful scrap transfer interrogation'... Alright. We found nothing and left you innocent citizens alone... yes, definitely much easier to fake. Move along!"</text>
					<!-- <remove name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM"/> -->
					
					<choice>
						<text>We won't make you say it twice!</text>
						<event/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	
