<event name="RKS_EXIT_PIRATE_TRINITY_AMBUSH">
	<text>Just as you were about to jump, a serious warship in pirate colors come out of hiding, followed by more pirates.
		"Forgetting something? A lil' business meeting that YOU asked for, maybe? Have you no honor??! You can't just make a bunch of cutthroats waste their time. Now die, fool!"
		
		Looks like the pirates didn't appreciate you not coming to your own Pirate Trinity reunion, and in order to leave you'll have to beat this Elite while its associates provide fire support!
	</text>
	<clearJumpEvent/>

	<!-- Only possible after Gatekeeper fights thanks to multiShipFix in hyperspace.xml.append -->
	<ship load="SHIP_PIRATE_ELITE_STARGROVE" hostile="true"/>
	<environment type="PDS" target="player"/>

	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Oh, that's what the weird feeling was about.</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>

